description:
A web-application that loads a datafile from the HDX Repository and display the content of it. 

The application was developed by [Dominik Kalisch](http://www.kalisch.biz/) and will soon be made open-source through his [GitHub account](https://github.com/dkalisch/).
title: Data Explorer
